songs.title: Me & My Boyfriend
songs.lyrics:
Me and my boyfriend
We are a new kind of fun
He dyed his hair black
I dye my hair platinum

We all wear black
We are trying to be fine
Elvis and Marilyn
Marilyn
Marilyn
Marilyn
Marilyn

Me and my boyfriend
We are lying a lot
We don’t leave often
We live our life as a song
